window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I knew I wanted her the first time I saw her. Only problem? She can’t be my mate.</p> <p>I’m a son of a traitor and former Alpha, and I know it’s the legacy people see.</p> <p>But I must be the Alpha of my Pack and protect them from the new threat to our world: Vampires.Valac and the others are still in the shadows, and we must find their lairs before we lose more than we already have.</p> <p>Only every time the enemy attacks, Skye puts herself in jeopardy. I’m the dominant wolf, but she’s the one with the most to lose.</p> <p>She’s the Pack princess. The daughter of legends.</p> <p>And I know she’s not my mate.</p> <p>But I want her. I need her. And now I must convince my wolf. Or break the most sacred rules of the moon goddess.</p> <p>Again.</p>"; 
